        "data": "<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>As part of Liferay Cloud's ongoing commitment to provide the highest degree of support we are introducing a services suite version number. This version number details a snapshot of the officially released service docker images that should be used.</p>\n<p>Our product development and infrastructure has gone through three major phases. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.0.0 -&gt; home grown</li>\n<li>2.0.0 -&gt; docker swarm</li>\n<li>3.0.0 -&gt; kubernetes</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>DXP Stack 2019.20.1</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 118px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 148px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 157px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 498px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Backup</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.0.4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/backup:</span>3.0.0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.0.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 41.2222px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/database:</span>3.0.0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">CI</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 148px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.0.4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 157px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3.0.0</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/jenkins:</span>2.164.1-3.0.0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Liferay</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.5.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px;\ntext-align: center;\nvertical-align: middle;\nheight: 48px;\">\n<p><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.0.0-sp10-fp81-3.0.0</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">iferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1.0-ga1-fp10-3.0.0</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.0.7</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span>feraycloud/elasticsearch:6.1.4-3.0.0</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Webserver</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">2.1.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 118px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 36px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">3.0.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 498px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">l<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">iferaycloud/nginx:<span>1.14.1-3.0.0</span></span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Change Log</h2>\n<p>Make services compatible with Kubernetes infrastructure</p>\n<div id=\"root\">\n<div id=\"layout-main\" class=\"styles__main___3qLof\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<div id=\"module-repository\">\n<div id=\"module-repository-detail\" class=\"styles__content___3u8I1\">\n<div class=\"styles__body___T4UNY\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"styles__newDesign___Ly9u3 styles__card___1d1uz\">\n<div class=\"styles__content___1LQdY \">\n<div class=\"styles__listItem___3AGFb\">\n<div class=\"styles__titleRow___KysRo\">\n<div id=\"root\">\n<div id=\"layout-main\" class=\"styles__main___3qLof\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<div>\n<div id=\"module-repository\">\n<div id=\"module-repository-detail\" class=\"styles__content___3u8I1\">\n<div class=\"styles__body___T4UNY\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"styles__newDesign___Ly9u3 styles__card___1d1uz\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"root\">\n<div id=\"layout-main\" class=\"styles__main___3qLof\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<div>\n<div id=\"module-repository\">\n<div id=\"module-repository-detail\" class=\"styles__content___3u8I1\">\n<div class=\"styles__body___T4UNY\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div